\begin_layout Paragraph
Environmental stressors
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
I aim to explore the role of nongenetic effects across a number of environmental
 stresses, as we currently do not know whether nongenetic effects are restricted
 to specific forms of stress or have a general function over different stresses.
 I will use the following three stresses: (i) temperature, (ii) osmotic
 stress, (iii) oxidative stress.
 All these stresses have the advantage that they have been rather well explored
 in 
\begin_inset ERT
status open

\begin_layout Plain Layout


\backslash
emph{Sz.
 pombe}
\end_layout

\end_inset

 at the within-generational level (e.g., 
\begin_inset CommandInset citation
LatexCommand citep
key "Chen2003,Madrid2006,Lackner2012"

\end_inset

).
 
\end_layout

